NAME
    Color::HSV::Util - Utilities related to HSV color space

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.003 of Color::HSV::Util (from Perl
    distribution Color-HSV-Util), released on 2021-08-06.

SYNOPSIS
     use Color::HSV::Util qw(
                           hsl2hsv
                           hsv2hsl
                           hsv2rgb
                           rgb2hsv
     );

DESCRIPTION
    HSV color value is written using this notation:

     H S V

    that is, three floating point numbers separated by a single space.
    Examples:

     0 1 1                     # red (RGB ff0000)
     120 0.498 1               # light green (RGB 80ff80)

FUNCTIONS
  hsl2hsv
  hsv2hsl
  hsv2rgb
  rgb2hsv
